,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"574d9715d194bf9efdca39a3f4c4dd60cd44479a","tid":531264,"uid":157697,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T15:28:45.000Z","msg":"利申：自諗<br />\n<br />\n分開4組數睇<br />\n第1組：1，3，2，<br />\n第2組：5，7，6，<br />\n第3組13，19，14，<br />\n第4組：33，？，？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每組第3個字：來自第1個字+1，就如第1組1+1=2，第2組5+1=6，第3組13+1=14<br />\n<br />\n而每組第1個字：來自前一組第3個字+第4個字，就如第1組3+2=5，第2組7+6=13，第3組19+14=33<br />\n<br />\n最後係每組第2個字：來自第1個字+前一組第3個字，就如第2組5+2=7，第3組6+13=19<br />\n<br />\n因此，第4組應該係33，47，34............."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T21:16:38.000Z","msg":"This can be simplified to:<br />\nGiven T(1) = 1, T(2) = 3<br />\n<br />\nT(n) = {<br />\n   T(n-2)+1, if n = 3k,<br />\n   T(n-1)+T(n-2), otherwise<br />\n}"},{"pid":"3bb4bd3a66301b5941deee85a103906384569a42","tid":531264,"uid":8954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T21:37:05.000Z","msg":"認真 呢類係大學year1 logic數<br />\n點解可以係小學問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369100d5b3a42764ac5983393ca4d8a2339cc45f","tid":531264,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T21:39:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d74cf9ccc2c327388875fe3f761e4ec3630e0573","tid":531264,"uid":34058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T21:44:03.000Z","msg":"簡單數列 等比 等差果啲唔係都初中先教咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定我記錯<br />\n覺得呢啲好考數感<br />\n最好感受到同天生數叻嘅人差距<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}